Package com.project.RabbitRun.eventHandlers

Class KeyHandler

java.lang.Object
com.project.RabbitRun.eventHandlers.KeyHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyListener, EventListener
public class KeyHandler extends Object implements KeyListener
The KeyHandler class handles keyboard inputs for controlling player movement and game state changes. It listens for key events and updates corresponding movement flags based on the keys pressed or released.
